videos.description: Jae Crowder forces the Bucks to take a timeout as he throws down a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Crowder flushes fast-break dunk

videos.description: A Suns fan flexes his cash during Giannis Antetokounmpo's free throw attempts in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Suns fan flashes $100s during Giannis' free throws) 2021/7/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Suns fan flashes $100s during Giannis' free throws

videos.description: Devin Booker throws down over Giannis Antetokounmpo, but the referees had already blown the play dead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker's dunk on Giannis waved off) 2021/7/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker's dunk on Giannis waved off

videos.description: Bobby Portis flexes after he outworks the Suns' defense to grab the rebound and get the second-chance bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Portis battles for the board and the bucket) 2021/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Portis battles for the board and the bucket

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo uses a spin move to get into the middle of the paint and lofts in a jump hook over Deandre Ayton.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis spins to get a bucket over Ayton) 2021/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis spins to get a bucket over Ayton

videos.description: An exhausted Khris Middleton uses a step-back move on Jae Crowder to knock down the clutch bucket and draw the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Middleton drains and-1 step-back on Crowder) 2021/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Middleton drains and-1 step-back on Crowder

videos.description: Khris Middleton knocks down a step-back 3-pointer in the face of the defense to push the Bucks' lead to 120-112.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play ('More Middleton magic!' Middleton drains clutch triple) 2021/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: 'More Middleton magic!' Middleton drains clutch triple

videos.description: Devin Booker fades away to knock down a big-time 3-pointer over the contest of Jrue Holiday to cut the Bucks' lead late in the fourth.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker drains sweet fadeaway 3 over Holiday) 2021/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker drains sweet fadeaway 3 over Holiday

videos.description: Jrue Holiday picks Devin Booker's pocket and then throws a lob to Giannis Antetokounmpo for the alley-oop.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis soars for alley-oop dagger after Holiday's crucial steal) 2021/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis soars for alley-oop dagger after Holiday's crucial steal

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo walks Malika Andrews through Jrue Holiday's crucial steal on Devin Booker as the Bucks are on the verge of an NBA title.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Giannis Antetokounmpo talks ‘big-time’ Jrue Holiday steal) 2021/7/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis Antetokounmpo talks 'big-time' Jrue Holiday steal

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo racks up 32 points, 9 rebounds and 6 assists to lead the Bucks to a 3-2 series lead over the Suns with a 123-119 win in Game 5.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Bucks stun Suns in Game 5 thriller) 2021/07/17 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Bucks stun Suns in Game 5 thriller
